            <p>Money Unit = 0 return amount in XRC<br />Money Unit = 1 return amount in Satoshi</p>
            <pre>https://explorer.xrhodium.org/api/data/gettotalsupply?moneyUnit=0</pre>
            <p><strong>Example of result:</strong></p>
            <pre class="prettyprint">
"1115545"
</pre>
